scenes.description: Cecilia Immergreen presents her 'Multi Case' merchandise.
Raora Panthera presents the hololive English -Justice- '3D Acrylic Stand' merchandise.
Elizabeth Rose Bloodflame presents her 'Paper Knife & Acrylic Stand' merchandise.
Gigi Murin presents her 'Hand In Cushion' merchandise.
Cecilia Immergreen presents her 'Pouch & Socks' merchandise.
Raora Panthera presents her 'Pencil Case & Keychain' merchandise.
The group makes final announcements regarding merchandise availability, their first live concert, and a new music video.
